# Urdu language in the United Kingdom|Urdu 269,000 or 0.5%
# Bengali language|Bengali (with Sylheti language|Sylheti and Chittagonian language|Chittagonian) 221,000 or 0.4%
# Gujarati language|Gujarati 213,000 or 0.4% 
# Arabic 159,000 or 0.3%
